Appendix A: How to apply these terms to your program
====================================================

To show that your source file is licensed under this license, either
put the complete license in each file OR, preferrably, this short
reference:

/* Copyright (c) YYYY nameOfYourCompany. All rights reserved. */

/* This  program is licensed under  the CPL. Basically, this means you
   can do  most anything you like, as  long  as you give  credit where
   due. Consult the file XXXXXXXX (included with this package) for the
   full conditions. */

